Scaling        Horizontal (sharding)      Vertical (mostly)
Relationships  Embedding / References     JOINs
Transactions   Supported (v4.0+)          Native & mature
Query Language MongoDB Query Language     SQL (standardized)
Speed (writes) Very fast                   Moderate
Data integrity App-level                    DB-level (constraints)
